Senior Backend Software Engineer with Reputation.com

Dear Brian, 

I found your profile and am really impressed with your background and experience. I am currently recruiting for a senior backend software engineer and I think you would excel in this position. Reputation.com offers a unique work environment where innovation, growth and personal development is fully embraced. The link for the position is in the link below. If you are interested and would like more information about this position, please email me at hsui@reputation.com with your resume and a few dates and times you are available for a quick call. Thank you and I look forward to your response.
